{"results":[{"aya":"162","id":3094,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"我对于你们确是一个忠实的使者。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"163","id":3095,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"故你们应当敬畏真主，应当服从我。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"164","id":3096,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"我不为传达使命而向你们索取任何报酬；我的报酬，只归全世界的主负担。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"165","id":3097,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"你们怎么要与众人中的男性交接，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"166","id":3098,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"而舍弃你们的主所为你们创造的妻子呢？其实，你们是犯罪的民众。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"167","id":3099,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"他们说：鲁特啊！如果你不停止，你必遭放逐。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"168","id":3100,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"他说：我的确痛恨你们的行为。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":33,"previousPage":"/zh/s026-23.json","nextPage":"/zh/s026-25.json"}}